NB: 
- untuk mengubah password akun pegawai tertentu


Header
- Content-Type  : application/json
- Authorization : Bearer <token>


url      : http://localhost:{port}/api/employee/password
type     : POST
params   : {
    "employeeId": 1,
    "oldPassword": "123",
    "currentPassword": "456",
}


RESPONSE
--------
{
	"code": 200,
	"status": "OK",
	"data": null,
	"paging": null,
	"errors": null,
}
